    "body": "I seem to have answered my own question. In particular, this issue is fixed by manually specifying `--enable-transparent-visuals --disable-gpu` when launching electron, and has to do with some issues with translucent visuals. The reason it worked on Linux was that I was already doing this in my launcher (I just forgot why!). Closing :)"
